          "reviewBody": "\"GG International School\" is an awesome education institution. The teachers there are all well-trained. They have a strong leadership in the form of Principal Mrs. Bharti Bhagwani, who is an Iron Lady. With each passing year, GGIS students achieve success in leaps and bounds. What I value the most is the cultural and the moral values passed on to the students. I'm a parent of a GGIS student and have seen tremendous growth in my own child in the past 6 years.\nThank you GGIS!",
