            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "We changed my daughter's school mid-term to GGIS and it's one of the best decisions we've made. The school excels in every aspect of education right from the best of teachers in each subject to the best facilities. They have tons of extra curricular activities and focus on each genre of a growing kid equally. Parents are kept up-to-date with each and every day aspect and they also have a quarterly update on the syllabus and curriculum.",
